Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.04,0:03:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,那是因为你太兴奋了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.84,0:03:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,不过真是太好了，小石
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.41,0:03:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,还好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.59,0:03:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么了？阿跨
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.12,0:03:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,无精打采的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.62,0:03:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,大概是因为那个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.62,0:03:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,因为只有自己没有人陪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.53,0:03:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,无法诚心的祝福别人\N感觉到自己器量的狭窄
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.76,0:03:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,拼命的想要挤出一个笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.30,0:03:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,偏偏理性无法控制感性
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.77,0:03:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,亦即，所谓的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.14,0:03:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,才不是这样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.07,0:03:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我说阿跨啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.21,0:03:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你就别想高攀瑞穗老师了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.61,0:03:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,就近忍耐一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.24,0:03:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,就近？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.92,0:03:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,森野的确长得很可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.62,0:03:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,别喜欢上我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.42,0:03:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.46,0:03:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.03,0:04:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,漂介，你也是因为就近\N才跟我在一起的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.73,0:04:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,才不是呢，你不要误会
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.60,0:04:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.84,0:04:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,不是啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.91,0:04:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,那你喜欢我哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.64,0:04:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,真拿他们没辄
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.08,0:04:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,这个嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.95,0:04:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,果然是因为“就近”的关系
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.38,0:04:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,不是啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.62,0:04:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,季节已经来到\N不需要这个的时候了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.32,0:04:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.13,0:04:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.56,0:04:30.19,Default,,0,0,0,,小桂的朋友\N那位个子小小的女生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.26,0:04:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,她也得了同样的病啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.30,0:04:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,不想让森野停滞下来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.37,0:04:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我非常了解小桂的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.74,0:04:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,所以这种状况\N可能会持续一段时间
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.25,0:04:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.15,0:04:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,既然瑞穗老师都这么说了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.28,0:04:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,可是，这样好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.29,0:04:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,这是小桂所希望的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.76,0:05:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是说小桂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.26,0:05:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,这也是瑞穗老师你所希望的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.46,0:05:05.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我是个大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.07,0:05:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀，有什么关系呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.44,0:05:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,女人在心爱的人面前
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.77,0:05:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,稍微任性一点也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.84,0:05:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,可是，我是个老师
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.72,0:05:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,这样啊，你们进行得很顺利是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.32,0:05:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.09,0:05:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,那么，谢谢惠顾
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.73,0:05:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.77,0:05:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,对了\N上次我说的是真的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.77,0:05:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,把头发剪短，胡须剃干净
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.40,0:05:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,一定会很有女人缘的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.21,0:05:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.75,0:05:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我明白了，瑞穗老师
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.78,0:06:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,那就先让小桂住我这里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.35,0:06:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.39,0:06:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托你了…是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.48,0:06:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,喂，我是森野
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.51,0:06:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,啊，森野，是我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.92,0:06:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,身体情况如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.32,0:06:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.65,0:06:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,没有发病的征兆
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.65,0:06:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.22,0:06:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.06,0:06:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,倒是，你自己呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.89,0:06:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你在勉强你自己吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.43,0:06:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,没有这回事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.26,0:06:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,缘川是个好女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.06,0:06:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,身材也蛮不错的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.17,0:06:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,而且她很喜欢我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.28,0:06:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.81,0:06:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,没有，没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.51,0:07:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,森野
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.38,0:07:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.45,0:07:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要前进
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.72,0:07:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,一定要向前进
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.72,0:07:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯，是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.99,0:08:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,可以牵手吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.29,0:08:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.83,0:08:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,总觉得夏天就要结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.43,0:08:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我好喜欢夏天
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.84,0:08:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,小桂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.17,0:08:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,啊，对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.67,0:08:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,反正夏天还会再来嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.08,0:08:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,到了明年，一定会再来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.91,0:08:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.92,0:08:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,,不过
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.28,0:08:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,今年的夏天，只有今年会来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.87,0:09:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,忘了拿给他
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.41,0:09:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,小桂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.72,0:09:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,喂，我是森野
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.62,0:09:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,啊，是我，草薙桂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.22,0:09:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,草薙啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.89,0:09:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我马上下去，你等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.40,0:09:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,你不用这么担心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.97,0:09:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,这个我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.74,0:09:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,可是还是会担心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.27,0:09:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你不相信我吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.91,0:09:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,因为总觉得你无法掌握
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.71,0:09:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,啊，对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.11,0:09:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我就是这种个性
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.35,0:09:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,或者应该说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.49,0:09:55.89,Default,,0,0,0,,自从生病之后\N变得有点喜欢挖苦人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.96,0:09:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我明白这种感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.36,0:09:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.86,0:10:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,不要紧，你摸摸看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.06,0:10:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,心脏跳得很稳对不对？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.67,0:10:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.40,0:10:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你好纯情喔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.54,0:10:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,请你说我是个有常识的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.71,0:10:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,不过，健康就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.91,0:10:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我是真的这么认为
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.88,0:10:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.81,0:10:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,如果能早一点认识你，我…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.95,0:10:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,一定是老天爷让我们相逢的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.75,0:10:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,同病相怜的两个人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.39,0:10:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,草薙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.43,0:10:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,小桂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.66,0:10:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,缘川\N小石
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.16,0:10:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,原…原来是这么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.93,0:10:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,不是的，你误会了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.94,0:10:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我们是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.20,0:10:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你说谎！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.11,0:10:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我知道\N你的心一直不在我身上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.34,0:10:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我观察你很久了\N我看得出来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.98,0:10:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我还以为你是一直忘不了\N之前喜欢的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.38,0:10:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,结果根本不是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.15,0:11:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,根本不是这样嘛！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.92,0:11:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,缘川，缘川
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.72,0:11:05.49,Default,,0,0,0,,小石，小石
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.99,0:11:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,不行，不要停止
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.56,0:11:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,缘川的误会，我会去说清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.46,0:11:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,所以你千万不要停滞！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.43,0:11:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉我缘川可能会去的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.96,0:11:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,她果然在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.32,0:11:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,真不愧是亲密的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.96,0:11:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,不要开玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.29,0:11:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我没有这个意思
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.40,0:11:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,那我过去找她
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.23,0:11:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,好坚强喔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.30,0:11:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你好坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.10,0:11:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,会吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.47,0:11:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,不过我的确希望变得坚强一点
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.41,0:11:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,嗨
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.24,0:11:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,小桂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.48,0:12:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你愿意听我说吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.65,0:12:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.75,0:12:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我跟森野的事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.65,0:12:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,其实我只是去找她\N谈你的事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.52,0:12:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我才不相信呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.82,0:12:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,那你要我怎么做？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.39,0:12:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么做你才肯相信？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.53,0:12:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,吻我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.17,0:12:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,,吻我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.08,0:12:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,好，我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.56,0:12:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,老…老师
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.63,0:12:52.89,Default,,0,0,0,,瑞穗老师
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.64,0:12:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,小桂，你的手…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.07,0:13:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.58,0:13:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,老师，为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.75,0:13:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.15,0:13:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.92,0:13:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,小桂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.73,0:13:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,这是怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.36,0:13:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么瑞穗老师会哭呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.16,0:13:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.70,0:13:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起，缘川，我马上回来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.57,0:13:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.07,0:13:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,小桂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.04,0:13:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,小石
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.31,0:13:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,小苺
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.71,0:13:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我全部跟你说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.51,0:13:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,不，我似乎非说不可
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.62,0:13:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我到底在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.69,0:13:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,居然会做这种事，真是笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.39,0:13:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然很笨，可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.00,0:13:58.99,Default,,0,0,0,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.60,0:14:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.54,0:14:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,小桂跟小苺罹患同一种病？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.35,0:14:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.78,0:14:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,听了你跟草薙的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.78,0:14:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我就在想\N你一定哭得很伤心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.95,0:14:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,真的很受不了，所以就发病了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.16,0:14:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,草薙知道了以后，为了我…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.30,0:14:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,所以他才会打电话给我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.23,0:14:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,那么，小桂喜欢的人是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.17,0:14:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我想可能是瑞穗老师
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.11,0:14:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我刚才也察觉到了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.27,0:14:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,他们两个\N不是已经在交往了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.68,0:14:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,这个我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.25,0:14:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,小桂有喜欢的人\N为了你而离开她
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.38,0:14:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,原来他是抱着\N这种心情跟我见面的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.42,0:14:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我不要这样子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.16,0:14:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,这样我不就变成坏人了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.03,0:15:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.03,0:15:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,可是我不想看你哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.53,0:15:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么？\N你太多管闲事了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.83,0:15:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起，对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.67,0:15:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,小苺，你怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.54,0:15:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,不要停！向前进！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.64,0:15:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,可是，我…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.35,0:15:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.18,0:15:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.55,0:15:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想看到你哭
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.02,0:15:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,不要瞧不起人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.19,0:15:33.89,Default,,0,0,0,,就算我被人家甩了\N就算我哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.96,0:15:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,要我勉强装出笑容\N也没有意义吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.80,0:15:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你是我的好朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.83,0:15:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,这种时候\N你应该要陪我哭才对
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.73,0:15:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,小石
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.97,0:15:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我要哭，陪着我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.84,0:15:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,小石…好，我陪你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.48,0:15:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.08,0:15:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我才应该说谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.52,0:16:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,喂，小桂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.62,0:16:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,小…桂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.14,0:16:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,在哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.41,0:16:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,求求你，玛利耶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.35,0:16:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你听到我讲话\N请回应我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.65,0:16:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我想见老师
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.96,0:16:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我好想见她
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.49,0:16:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,所以，把我转移到\N老师所在的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.60,0:16:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,这是…这是…对我而言
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.87,0:16:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,是最优先事项
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.90,0:16:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,这是最优先事项
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.32,0:17:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,好漂亮的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.73,0:17:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,得感谢阿实叔他们才行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.45,0:17:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,小桂，你怎么会到这里来？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.52,0:17:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,老师！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.62,0:17:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,玛利耶，空间转移\N这是最优先事项喔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.00,0:17:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,这是最优先事项！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.00,0:17:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,求求你，听我的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.74,0:17:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,老师！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.80,0:17:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,老师！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.24,0:18:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.41,0:18:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下！等一下！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.15,0:18:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.28,0:18:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,老师，不要这样啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.72,0:18:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.56,0:18:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.60,0:18:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,讨厌讨厌讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.40,0:18:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我最讨厌你！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.00,0:18:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,这样啊，我想也是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.17,0:18:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.31,0:18:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,这样我就可以放得下了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.98,0:18:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,这样我就能前进了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.75,0:18:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我一定能够前进
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.32,0:18:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,可是我喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.02,0:18:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,喜欢，喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.32,0:18:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,小桂，我喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.46,0:18:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,小桂，我喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.93,0:19:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,老…老师
