Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.96,0:19:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.97,0:19:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.94,0:19:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,可恶，气死我了
