Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.43,0:20:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我也想跟你在一起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.86,0:20:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,可是，可是，可是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.40,0:20:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,可是，可是…
